# CUT ccommand

character level par processing karne k liye use hoti hai cut command
# first character in every file
> cut -c1 data
# first and 5th character
> cut -c1,5 data
# first 5 chars
cut -c1-5 data

# we can also fetch CSV from cut command using delimiter i.e. -d flag
> cut -d, -f 2 data
